module multi_8bit (
    input [7:0] A,
    input [7:0] B,
    output reg [15:0] product
);

always @(*) begin
    product = 16'd0;
    for (integer i = 0; i < 8; i = i + 1) begin
        if (B[i]) begin
            product = product + (A << i);
        end
    end
end

endmodule
